Package arduino

This package contains all of the classes necessary to communicate with an Arduino in a fingerprint robot.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    This class represents a command.
    NARFSTR
    Represents a Networked Automated Rolled Fingerprint Scanner Test Robot (NARFSTR).
    NetworkRobotCom
    This class represents a connection to an Arduino over Ethernet.
    Robot
    This class represents an Arduino.
    RobotCom<T extends java.nio.channels.ByteChannel>
    This class represents a connection to an Arduino.
    RobotInfo
    Contains a robot's type, mac address, and connection location.
    SerialChannel
    A channel for a serial connection.
    SerialRobotCom
    This class represents a connection to an Arduino over USB.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SENSOR_TYPE
    The list of sensor types on the Arduino.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    RobotCommandExecutionException
    The exception throw if there is an error executing a command.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Bounds
    Represents the bounds on an integer parameter.
    RobotCommand
    Used to annotate a method that is a robot command.
